{"tid":2241173,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"做運動見過最嚴重嘅受傷係點","createTime":"2020-10-13T06:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T08:13:32.000Z","uid":117802,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0171f234d7dc4a0c3760f0d360921c9557e770c8","tid":2241173,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:47:31.000Z","msg":"普遍啲嘅見過龍門救波落地落得唔好甩骹，要call白車<br />\n<br />\n又見過隊友想轉身但係隻重心腳俾對手頂住，種死咗喺地下，搞到一轉身就痛到大嗌瞓咗喺地下，結果係整傷韌帶，成兩年幾都好唔返哂<br />\n<br />\n睇完段籃球片頂人膝頭哥就覺得條友好危險<br />\n<br />\n未現場見過人斷腳，如果唔係個畫面實離唔開個腦"},{"pid":"592b2a6a53ab8a7d1b1c1224fa0771b5490e105d","tid":2241173,"uid":7232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:50:05.000Z","msg":"踢波磨甩粒lin"},{"pid":"4d0779454c2434eeeca655e1e99ef4bb98a0ebc5","tid":2241173,"uid":7232,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:50:18.000Z","msg":"話說佢唔著衫踢<br />\n之後就入左波<br />\n跟住學D足球員胸貼地咁滑地下<br />\n點知一滑個下<br />\n捽甩左粒lin<br />\n我地成班FD見到已經笑到Hi Hi<br />\n咁我地就叫白車啦<br />\n聽電話個個都笑住問我地係邊到咁<br />\n之後去到醫院<br />\n個醫生問粒LIN去左邊<br />\n我個FD話:粒LIN有用架??唔向左走向右走係呀??<br />\n粒LIN而家應該仲係球場到<br />\n咁返去搵已經唔見左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個FD就係咁冇左粒LIN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124fff32e1efac32702dc7ddbc27c929b4d8116f","tid":2241173,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:51:21.000Z","msg":"小腿骨開放性骨折，斷骨插咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31215eb3b384173862758da1ee0689cb0ae3f0a8","tid":2241173,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:51:27.000Z","msg":"外國gym撚見過條瘦撚鬼佬深蹲太大重量斷左腳"},{"pid":"8d0d54cd9233b2184f3d497220088108b197328c","tid":2241173,"uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:51:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說佢唔著衫踢<br />\n之後就入左波<br />\n跟住學D足球員胸貼地咁滑地下<br />\n點知一滑個下<br />\n捽甩左粒lin<br />\n我地成班FD見到已經笑到仆街<br />\n咁我地就叫白車啦<br />\n聽電話個個都笑住問我地係邊到咁<br />\n之後去到醫院<br />\n個醫生問粒LIN去左邊<br />\n我個FD話:粒LIN有用架??唔撚係呀??<br />\n粒LIN而家應該仲係球場到<br />\n咁返去搵已經唔見左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我個FD就係咁冇左粒LIN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f6a54fba71f398004ac28d3e24bec9a1b1013afa","tid":2241173,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:51:49.000Z","msg":"射完波發現腳指公斷咗，睇着對白飯魚一路變紅。"},{"pid":"4a071770b7a8b2e29d6c049b7e7414952cac1e6a","tid":2241173,"uid":25559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:52:07.000Z","msg":"見過斷手 果個就係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e2eacd1b7f7b0bd7dd3be06b76c77f469fae7b","tid":2241173,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6a54fba71f398004ac28d3e24bec9a1b1013afa","tid":2241173,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:51:49.000Z","msg":"射完波發現腳指公斷咗，睇着對白飯魚一路變紅。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:52:24.000Z","msg":"嘩好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721703f5ceb4bd483e32b0027ae8aa23a89596ba","tid":2241173,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"124fff32e1efac32702dc7ddbc27c929b4d8116f","tid":2241173,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:51:21.000Z","msg":"小腿骨開放性骨折，斷骨插咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"睇唔睇到點整親<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06f561090234919e3bf633247cec14d9a8fa5ee","tid":2241173,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31215eb3b384173862758da1ee0689cb0ae3f0a8","tid":2241173,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:51:27.000Z","msg":"外國gym撚見過條瘦撚鬼佬深蹲太大重量斷左腳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T06:53:06.000Z","msg":"<im